            <thetext>During the automated test runs, the testrunner application will frequently hang right after loading the qx.test.EditDistance package. The status bar displays &quot;Preparing...&quot; but the tests don&#39;t start. The GUI is responsive, and clicking &quot;Stop&quot; followed by &quot;Run&quot; causes the tests to execute and the simulation to continue normally. This seems to be limited to Windows (XP and Vista) but not to any specific browser.</thetext>
